@node Main "GridBlock - Documentation"

                             'GridBlock' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'GridBlock' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you try to 'unlock'
all 4 corners of a 7 by 7 spaces game board. To do this, you
have to move horizontal and vertical bars, so the empty space
is moved to each corner of the board.

  One complication to the game is that each of the 24 bars
occupies 2 spaces, and a bar can only move in the direction
indicated by it: a horizontal bar can move horizontally and a
vertical bar can move vertically... towards the empty space.

  Have fun!

